=================================================  -->
<subsubsection xml:id="lec-mantenerBalance-sintesis" component="profesor">
  <shorttitle><custom ref="synthesis-leccion-titulo"/></shorttitle>
  <title><custom ref="synthesis-leccion-titulo"/></title>
  <title component="profesor"><nbsp/>(15 mins)</title>
  <p>[@@@@@@@]</p>
  <p>
    Display the two equations <m>5x = 8</m> and <m>5 + x = 8</m>. Ask students to draw a hanger to match each equation. Then have them work with a partner to solve the equation alongside finding the unknown value on the hanger. Ask students to compare the two strategies and discuss how they are alike and how they are different.
  </p>

</subsubsection>



